        <h2>
            知日·日本禅的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 16 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6250876">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6250876/" class="title-link">浅尝辄止论禅说道</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6250876"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/williamsoar/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1227902-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/williamsoar/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">我非衣</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-08-28"
      class="main-meta">2013-08-28 15:34:15</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6250876_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  《知日·日本禅》是一本很驳杂的书，前半部分讲了日本禅的历史发展，而后半部分讲了茶道、花道、剑道等的故事。然而，我觉得这本书最大的问题不是讲的多与不多，而是没有讲到大家都关注的点。 “知日”系列一直都是以引荐日本文化为己任的杂志书，所以，我可以理解本书不需要什...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/6250876/#comments">(3回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">4有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6250876_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6250876_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6121525">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6121525/" class="title-link">了解日本禅</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6121525"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/gimmy/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2703803-13.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/gimmy/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">果子林001</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-06-19"
      class="main-meta">2013-06-19 18:25:36</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6121525_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这期日本禅，内容厚重丰富而庞杂，非常值得。前半本介绍日本禅的历史源流、现状，日本当代禅学大师，禅寺及禅修行僧的生活等，后半本内容则是禅文学艺术，建筑庭园、茶道花道、设计中的禅意、影视中的禅思、禅画、料理、动漫画作品、禅意摄影、制陶、木具器等等。几乎主要与日...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">7有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6121525_full" class="hidden">
